             was indicted for <rs id="t18141130-59-off368" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18141130-59-off368" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18141130-59-off368" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the 28th of October, twenty-five pound weight of lead, value 25 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18141130-59-victim668" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Spencer
                        <interp inst="t18141130-59-victim668" type="surname" value="Spencer"></interp>
