            </rs>.</p>
               <p>HUNTER, <rs id="t18141130-59-verdict373" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18141130-59-verdict373" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
